WEBVTT



00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:01.760
Matthew two.

00:00:03.392 --> 00:00:07.872
Now after Jesus was born in Bethlehem of Judea in the days of Herod the king,

00:00:08.256 --> 00:00:12.192
Behold, wise men from the east came to Jerusalem, saying,

00:00:12.992 --> 00:00:15.968
Where is he who has been born King of the Jews?

00:00:16.416 --> 00:00:19.008
For we saw his star as it rose.

00:00:20.128 --> 00:00:22.048
And have come to worship him

00:00:23.872 --> 00:00:26.784
When Herod the king heard this, he was troubled.

00:00:26.976 --> 00:00:29.056
And all Jerusalem with him,

00:00:29.920 --> 00:00:33.504
In assembling all the chief priests and the scribes and the people

00:00:33.536 --> 00:00:37.184
He inquired of them where the Christ was to be born.

00:00:38.144 --> 00:00:39.616
They told him

00:00:39.968 --> 00:00:41.984
in Bethlehem of Judea

00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:45.056
For so it is written by the prophet,

00:00:45.216 --> 00:00:50.304
And you, O Bethlehem, in the land of Judah, are by no means least among the rulers.

00:00:50.176 --> 00:00:51.488
of Judah.

00:00:51.968 --> 00:00:54.528
For from you shall come a ruler

00:00:54.784 --> 00:00:57.120
who will shepherd my people Israel.

00:00:58.784 --> 00:01:02.240
Then Herod summoned the wise men secretly.

00:01:02.464 --> 00:01:06.560
And ascertained from them what time the star had appeared

00:01:07.488 --> 00:01:09.152
And he sent them

00:01:09.888 --> 00:01:11.904
to Bethlehem saying

00:01:12.512 --> 00:01:17.024
Go and search diligently for the child and when you have found him

00:01:17.600 --> 00:01:19.104
Bring me word.

00:01:19.552 --> 00:01:21.568
that I too may come.

00:01:21.600 --> 00:01:23.168
And worship him.

00:01:25.024 --> 00:01:30.944
After listening to the king they went on their way and behold the star that they had seen

00:01:30.784 --> 00:01:32.256
When it rose

00:01:32.704 --> 00:01:34.336
Went before them.

00:01:35.104 --> 00:01:38.048
Until they came to rest over the place where

00:01:37.824 --> 00:01:39.424
The child was.

00:01:40.192 --> 00:01:44.416
When they saw the star, they rejoiced exceedingly with great joy.

00:01:45.184 --> 00:01:46.976
And going into the house

00:01:47.296 --> 00:01:49.664
They saw the child with his mother

00:01:49.632 --> 00:01:51.168
Mary, his mother,

00:01:51.264 --> 00:01:53.696
And they fell down and worshipped him.

00:01:55.104 --> 00:01:57.088
In opening their treasures

00:01:57.376 --> 00:01:59.040
They offered him gifts.

00:01:59.424 --> 00:02:01.920
Gold and frankincense and myrrh.

00:02:02.976 --> 00:02:06.944
And being worn in a dream not to return to Herod,

00:02:07.456 --> 00:02:10.592
They deported to their own country by another way.

00:02:15.936 --> 00:02:18.304
There are two ways to deal with Jesus.

00:02:20.160 --> 00:02:23.136
And I'm thinking of you tonight who are here

00:02:23.008 --> 00:02:27.232
who do not yet worship Jesus as your supreme treasure?

00:02:27.936 --> 00:02:30.144
There are two ways to deal with Jesus.

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:33.216
The way of Herod,

00:02:34.848 --> 00:02:36.864
And the way of the wise men.

00:02:39.232 --> 00:02:42.336
The way of herod is to try to get rid of jesus

00:02:43.712 --> 00:02:44.832
it was.

00:02:44.928 --> 00:02:46.656
Pure hypocrisy.

00:02:47.200 --> 00:02:53.024
When Herod said, "Bring me word about the child so I can come and worship him."

00:02:53.088 --> 00:02:55.936
He had no intention to worship Jesus.

00:02:56.224 --> 00:02:59.680
He intended to get rid of Jesus.

00:03:00.288 --> 00:03:02.816
In fact, within a matter of days,

00:03:02.976 --> 00:03:07.936
He would kill all the baby boys in Bethlehem, two years old and younger.

00:03:09.152 --> 00:03:12.352
But his effort to get rid of Jesus, as you know,

00:03:12.832 --> 00:03:13.984
Failed,

00:03:14.432 --> 00:03:16.384
And it will always

00:03:16.256 --> 00:03:17.216
They are.

00:03:18.048 --> 00:03:19.680
The way of Herod.

00:03:19.392 --> 00:03:20.960
Always

00:03:21.248 --> 00:03:22.464
Fails.

00:03:23.392 --> 00:03:25.824
Nowadays we can't kill Jesus.

00:03:27.200 --> 00:03:28.960
He's already died.

00:03:29.632 --> 00:03:31.072
and risen

00:03:30.976 --> 00:03:33.088
And rain's in heaven tonight

00:03:33.120 --> 00:03:34.944
Over this assembly

00:03:35.296 --> 00:03:37.024
And he will come again.

00:03:37.088 --> 00:03:39.296
So we have come up with war.

00:03:39.392 --> 00:03:43.136
Sophisticated ways, less violent,

00:03:42.976 --> 00:03:44.800
To get rid of Jesus.

00:03:45.248 --> 00:03:47.776
The most common way to get rid of Jesus

00:03:48.160 --> 00:03:51.264
Is to recreate him in our minds

00:03:51.744 --> 00:03:53.184
in a way that

00:03:52.992 --> 00:03:55.616
Gets rid of his claim upon us

00:03:56.128 --> 00:03:57.536
So he's

00:03:58.240 --> 00:03:59.744
A legend

00:04:00.224 --> 00:04:02.496
Or a mere moral teacher

00:04:02.976 --> 00:04:04.576
We're a prophet.

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:08.576
Or a symbol you can put on your wall, a symbol of hope.

00:04:08.416 --> 00:04:09.824
Around your neck.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:15.360
When I was in graduate school in Europe in

00:04:15.168 --> 00:04:20.160
the nineteen seventies there was a well-known book called jesus for atheists

00:04:21.696 --> 00:04:23.456
And lo and behold,

00:04:24.160 --> 00:04:25.888
Milan makovic

00:04:26.368 --> 00:04:29.664
Discovered at last after 2,000 years

00:04:29.760 --> 00:04:33.344
That the real Jesus is the perfect embodiment

00:04:33.344 --> 00:04:35.776
Of 20Th Century marxism

00:04:37.024 --> 00:04:38.656
And he's gone.

00:04:39.328 --> 00:04:41.376
And Marxism will go

00:04:42.784 --> 00:04:47.456
And we're still trying to get rid of Jesus by reinventing him in the

00:04:47.712 --> 00:04:51.424
Ideological images so that he just fits

00:04:51.616 --> 00:04:54.464
Instead of laying any claim on us

00:04:54.784 --> 00:04:55.872
At all.

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:59.776
The Herod way of dealing with Jesus

00:05:00.192 --> 00:05:04.896
It never worked. It never will work. You cannot get rid of Jesus.

00:05:05.568 --> 00:05:06.816
And my

00:05:06.656 --> 00:05:09.888
Please, with all of you tonight,

00:05:10.144 --> 00:05:11.552
Is that?

00:05:12.672 --> 00:05:14.144
You would not

00:05:14.080 --> 00:05:17.696
Spend your life trying to evade Jesus.

00:05:19.200 --> 00:05:20.608
Instead

00:05:22.464 --> 00:05:25.376
Deal with Jesus the way of the wise men

00:05:27.488 --> 00:05:28.928
Verse 11

00:05:28.960 --> 00:05:31.072
Going into the house.

00:05:32.192 --> 00:05:35.392
They saw the child with Mary, his mother,

00:05:35.456 --> 00:05:37.664
And they fell down,

00:05:38.176 --> 00:05:39.520
And worshiped

00:05:41.888 --> 00:05:43.648
Falling down.

00:05:43.680 --> 00:05:45.344
Signifies

00:05:46.336 --> 00:05:47.744
Submission

00:05:48.544 --> 00:05:50.944
And worship signifies

00:05:51.648 --> 00:05:53.184
Treasuring,

00:05:55.680 --> 00:05:57.632
You submit to him.

00:05:58.336 --> 00:05:59.872
As your king

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:02.688
And you worship him as your

00:06:02.976 --> 00:06:06.048
Treasure. that's the way of the wise men.

00:06:06.976 --> 00:06:09.248
It's a huge change in life.

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:10.656
When that happens

00:06:12.064 --> 00:06:14.464
None of us is born this way.

00:06:14.560 --> 00:06:17.216
Every one of us must change

00:06:17.600 --> 00:06:19.040
From the from the.

00:06:19.104 --> 00:06:20.576
Herod way

00:06:20.576 --> 00:06:22.784
To the wise men way.

00:06:23.264 --> 00:06:25.984
It's called by Jesus' new birth.

00:06:30.176 --> 00:06:31.936
When it happens

00:06:32.704 --> 00:06:34.336
You become

00:06:35.200 --> 00:06:37.920
A beneficiary of Christmas

00:06:38.880 --> 00:06:41.536
Design Christmas purpose

00:06:42.080 --> 00:06:44.832
And a few chapters later in matthew

00:06:44.896 --> 00:06:49.056
Jesus tells us why there's Christmas and why he came.

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:51.040
And what the design is

00:06:53.504 --> 00:06:57.120
The Son of Man came not to be served, but to serve.

00:06:57.728 --> 00:06:59.584
And to give his life

00:06:59.392 --> 00:07:01.696
As a ransom for many

00:07:04.320 --> 00:07:08.576
That's the best news in all the world for people like us.

00:07:08.640 --> 00:07:10.176
For two reasons

00:07:10.976 --> 00:07:17.728
One reason is that every one of us in this room tonight, doesn't matter where you're sitting and who you are,

00:07:18.432 --> 00:07:23.296
Every one of us in this room tonight is under the guilt and bondage of

00:07:23.104 --> 00:07:25.760
Of our own sinfulness against god

00:07:25.984 --> 00:07:27.680
We have a debt.

00:07:28.800 --> 00:07:30.368
And we cannot

00:07:30.592 --> 00:07:31.584
Pay it.

00:07:31.648 --> 00:07:33.728
You know you have a debt.

00:07:33.664 --> 00:07:40.128
You know you cannot pay. It's the witness of your conscience every late night when you're honest.

00:07:41.760 --> 00:07:45.376
That's why it's the best news in the world to hear

00:07:45.600 --> 00:07:47.712
God incarnate

00:07:48.800 --> 00:07:51.872
Jesus Christ, God in the flesh,

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:55.168
Look you in the eye and say, I came to pay it.

00:07:56.192 --> 00:07:57.952
I came to pay it.

00:07:58.944 --> 00:08:02.144
To give my life a ransom for many.

00:08:02.976 --> 00:08:06.656
That's why i came that's the meaning of christmas

00:08:08.384 --> 00:08:11.584
Here's the reason number two why it's the best news in the world

00:08:12.544 --> 00:08:17.248
When we experience the forgiveness and the liberation, the freedom,

00:08:17.760 --> 00:08:19.680
Through that ransom,

00:08:19.616 --> 00:08:22.272
We become beneficiaries

00:08:22.240 --> 00:08:26.016
For the rest of our lives and into eternity.

00:08:26.688 --> 00:08:28.448
Of the service

00:08:29.056 --> 00:08:31.200
Christ on our behalf.

00:08:31.136 --> 00:08:34.016
He works for us omnipotence

00:08:34.144 --> 00:08:35.936
Works for us

00:08:36.352 --> 00:08:38.944
The Son of Man came.

00:08:39.104 --> 00:08:41.184
not to be served

00:08:42.144 --> 00:08:43.712
But to serve

00:08:43.872 --> 00:08:45.120
Meaning

00:08:45.344 --> 00:08:47.264
Through all the pleasures,

00:08:47.552 --> 00:08:49.600
And through all the pain,

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:51.392
Of your life

00:08:51.904 --> 00:08:54.112
God in Christ

00:08:53.856 --> 00:08:55.616
Is working

00:08:55.904 --> 00:08:59.712
To bring you to everlasting happiness

00:08:59.584 --> 00:09:01.440
In the presence of god.

00:09:03.904 --> 00:09:08.032
This is the good news of great joy that the angels sang about.

00:09:08.928 --> 00:09:11.200
And it's yours tonight.

00:09:13.088 --> 00:09:14.144
If

00:09:14.208 --> 00:09:15.904
You will renounce

00:09:16.384 --> 00:09:17.984
The way of Herod,

00:09:18.816 --> 00:09:21.824
Getting rid of Jesus, evading Jesus.

00:09:22.528 --> 00:09:24.576
And embrace the way

00:09:25.632 --> 00:09:27.296
Of the wise men,

00:09:31.168 --> 00:09:33.440
The next song that we're going to sing

00:09:34.272 --> 00:09:36.544
in the bleak midwinter

00:09:36.800 --> 00:09:38.880
Ends on a note

00:09:40.128 --> 00:09:42.880
That will provide you with the

00:09:42.592 --> 00:09:46.272
Perfect moment in the pilgrimage of your life,

00:09:46.816 --> 00:09:50.080
To do what the wise men did.

00:09:51.808 --> 00:09:54.912
On that last note of this song

00:09:54.784 --> 00:09:58.144
you will be able to look Jesus in the eye

00:09:59.136 --> 00:10:00.736
With your hearts

00:10:00.544 --> 00:10:01.792
Eyes

00:10:01.792 --> 00:10:03.200
And say

00:10:04.448 --> 00:10:05.952
I surrender.

00:10:07.008 --> 00:10:09.760
My heart is no longer my own.

00:10:10.336 --> 00:10:12.672
My heart belongs to you.

00:10:13.248 --> 00:10:14.848
I bow down

00:10:15.296 --> 00:10:17.120
And I worship you.

00:10:17.024 --> 00:10:18.592
as my King.

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:20.800
And my treasure.

00:10:22.432 --> 00:10:25.984
And I pray that God would grant us all, every one of us,

00:10:26.144 --> 00:10:28.032
In this room the grace

00:10:28.864 --> 00:10:29.984
To do that.
